prisma_schema:
model admin_apilog {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime
  deletedAt DateTime?
  ip        String
  method    String
  path      String
  code      String
  ua        String
  userId    String
  userName  String
}

model admin_category {
  id         Int          @id @default(autoincrement())
  name       String
  admin_post admin_post[]
}

model admin_menu {
  id          Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  parentId    Int?
  label       String    @db.VarChar(32)
  path        String?   @db.VarChar(100)
  icon        String?   @db.LongText
  sort        Int
  level       Int
  name        String?   @db.VarChar(32)
  is_bottom   Int       @default(1) @db.UnsignedTinyInt
  create_time DateTime? @db.DateTime(0)
  perms       String?   @db.VarChar(100)
  menu_type   String?   @default("") @db.Char(1)
  api_id      String?   @default("") @db.VarChar(255)
}

model admin_post {
  id             Int             @id @default(autoincrement())
  title          String          @db.VarChar(32)
  poster         String?         @db.VarChar(255)
  published_at   DateTime?       @db.Date
  author         String          @db.VarChar(50)
  content        String?         @db.LongText
  cate           Int?
  auth           Int?
  user           user?           @relation(fields: [auth], references: [id], onDelete: NoAction, onUpdate: NoAction, map: "authorConn")
  admin_category admin_category? @relation(fields: [cate], references: [id], onDelete: NoAction, map: "post_id_fkey")

  @@index([auth], map: "authorConn")
  @@index([cate], map: "post_id_fkey")
}

model admin_salelog {
  id             Int            @id @default(autoincrement())
  shopName       String         @db.VarChar(50)
  day            DateTime       @db.DateTime(0)
  sales          Float
  typeId         Int
  admin_saletype admin_saletype @relation(fields: [typeId], references: [id], onDelete: NoAction, map: "SaleLog_typeId_fkey")

  @@index([typeId], map: "SaleLog_typeId_fkey")
}

model admin_saletype {
  id            Int             @id @default(autoincrement())
  name          String          @db.LongText
  createdAt     String          @db.LongText
  admin_salelog admin_salelog[]
}

model admin_sub {
  id          Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime
  deletedAt   DateTime?
  message     String
  create_role String
  target_role String
  type        String
}

model admin_visitlog {
  id        Int    @id @default(autoincrement())
  ip        String @db.LongText
  ua        String @db.LongText
  visitedAt String @db.LongText
}

model dic {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime
  deletedAt DateTime?
  isOpen    Boolean
}

model menu_role {
  id      Int @id @default(autoincrement())
  menu_id Int
  role_id Int

  @@unique([role_id, menu_id], map: "roleId")
}

model permission {
  id        BigInt    @id
  createdAt DateTime? @db.Date
  updatedAt DateTime? @db.Date
  method    String    @db.Char(10)
  path      String    @unique(map: "pathKey") @db.VarChar(50)
  enabled   Int       @default(1) @db.UnsignedTinyInt
}

model provider {
  owner         String  @db.VarChar(100)
  name          String  @unique(map: "UQE_provider_name") @db.VarChar(100)
  created_time  String? @db.VarChar(100)
  type          String? @db.VarChar(100)
  client_id     String? @db.VarChar(100)
  client_secret String? @db.VarChar(2000)
  sign_name     String? @db.VarChar(100)
  template_code String? @db.VarChar(100)

  @@id([owner, name])
}

model role {
  id     Int    @id @default(autoincrement())
  code   String @unique(map: "uniqueKey") @db.VarChar(20)
  remark String @db.VarChar(40)
}

model role_user {
  id      Int @id @default(autoincrement())
  role_id Int
  user_id Int

  @@unique([role_id, user_id], map: "role_user")
}

model user {
  id            Int          @id @default(autoincrement())
  created_at    DateTime?    @db.DateTime(0)
  name          String       @db.VarChar(32)
  avatar        String?      @db.VarChar(255)
  phone         String?      @db.Char(13)
  password_salt String?      @db.VarChar(100)
  password      String?      @db.VarChar(100)
  country_code  String?      @db.VarChar(6)
  password_type String?      @db.VarChar(100)
  user_id       String?      @db.VarChar(255)
  admin_post    admin_post[]
}

model verification_record {
  name         String   @id @db.VarChar(100)
  created_time String?  @db.VarChar(100)
  type         String?  @db.VarChar(10)
  user         String   @db.VarChar(100)
  provider     String   @db.VarChar(100)
  receiver     String   @db.VarChar(100)
  code         String   @db.VarChar(10)
  time         BigInt
  is_used      Boolean?
}
